		      <div class="description-box">
			      <h4>"The Smiles of Nature"</h4>
			      <p>The subject of this scene is a small ladybug resting peacefully on an abandoned snail shell nestled comfortably in some thick moss.
               </br></br>
Many different techniques were used in this image, including generating shapes from formulas, lens distortion, texture painting, and more. All were vital in achieving the final effect.</p>
		      </div>

